The remote control and its buttons will be made of rubber.
The case will be flat on top and curved on the bottom.
The remote will have push buttons outside , and an LCD and spinning wheel inside.
The remote will resemble a vegetable and be in bright vegetable colors.
It will have voice recognition , use a simple battery , and contain an advanced chip.
It will have standard on/off , channel-changing , numerical , and volume buttons , with a menu on the screen.
